'''札維耶·波瓦'''（{{lang-fr|Xavier Beauvois}}，{{bd|1967年|3月20日||}}）是一位[[法國|法國]][[導演|導演]]、劇作家。

==生平==
札維耶·波瓦以《[[別忘記你即將死去|別忘記你即將死去]]》（N'oublie pas que tu vas mourir）獲得1996年[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]評審團獎<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{Cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/3375/year/1995.html |title=Festival de Cannes: N'oublie pas que tu vas mourir |accessdate=2009-09-04 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2014-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016151854/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/3375/year/1995.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，札維耶·波瓦以《[[人神之間|人神之間]]》獲得[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]評審團大獎<ref>{{Cite news|last=Chang|first=Justin|date=23 May 2010|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118019731.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|title='Uncle Boonmee' wins Palme d'Or|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2010-09-08|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522193313/https://variety.com/article/VR1118019731.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last1=Hopewell|first1=John|last2=Keslassy|first2=Elsa|date=22 May 2010|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118019726.html?categoryId=3628&cs=1|title=Int'l critics bestow top honors at Cannes|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|accessdate=2010-05-24|archive-date=2010-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100810151341/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118019726.html?categoryid=3628&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並代表法國參加[[奧斯卡最佳外語片獎|奧斯卡最佳外語片獎]]<ref name="83rdAcademy">{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2010/20101013a.html |title=65 Countries Enter Race for 2010 Foreign Language Film Oscar |accessdate=2010-10-16 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001051912/https://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2010/20101013a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但並未入圍<ref name="Oscar Shortlist">{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2011/20110119.html |title=9 Foreign Language Films Continue to Oscar Race |accessdate=2011-01-19 |work=oscars.org |archive-date=2014-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001051828/https://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2011/20110119.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，札維耶·波瓦以《[[榮耀的代價|榮耀的代價]]》（La Rançon de la gloire）入圍[[第71屆威尼斯影展|第71屆威尼斯影展]]<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |title=International competition of feature films |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Venice |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083927/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |archivedate=2014年10月6日 }}</ref><ref name="Deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |title=Venice Film Festival Lineup Announced |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Deadline |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728233935/http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

